videos.description: Jack White misses the 3-pointer, but Zion Williamson is poorly marked and rises for the putback dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Zion flies in for putback jam) 2019/01/22

videos.headline: Zion flies in for putback jam

videos.description: Zion Williamson plays the give and go with Cam Reddish and absorbs the contact from Pitt's Terrell Brown for the difficult and-1 finish.
videos.headline: Zion hits tough and-1 layup

videos.description: Jared Wilson-Frame creates space with a pretty step back, before knocking down the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Pitt’s Wilson-Frame hits difficult step-back triple) 2019/01/22

videos.headline: Pitt's Wilson-Frame hits difficult step-back triple

videos.description: Zion Williamson starts the game 6-of-6 after tipping in R.J. Barrett's miss off the offensive rebound.
videos.headline: Zion cleans up Barrett's miss

videos.description: Zion Williamson grabs another offensive rebound, then muscles his way inside for the and-1 lay-in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Zion stays perfect with another and-1 layup) 2019/01/22

videos.headline: Zion stays perfect with another and-1 layup

videos.description: Zion Williamson goes 9-of-9 from the field, dropping 19 points against Pittsburgh in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Zion leads Duke with perfect 1st half) 2019/01/22 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Zion leads Duke with perfect 1st half

videos.description: Zion Williamson pokes the ball away, then sprints the other way for the high-rising one-handed flush.

videos.headline: Zion steals, then throws down dunk with authority

videos.description: Duke's defense forces a turnover, then Zion Williamson passes ahead to RJ Barrett for the slam.
